Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:41.46,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Homura-chan, were you aware?{ほむらちゃんは…知ってたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:46.14,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you inform anyone?{どうして教えてくれなかったの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:51.47,Homura,,0,0,0,,Because even though I have discussed it in the past, not a single person has believed me so far.{前もって話しても、信じてくれた人は今まで一人もいなかったわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:54.48,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Why does Kyubey do such an awful thing?{キュゥべえはどうしてこんなひどいことをするの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.98,Homura,,0,0,0,,That thing doesn't even think it's awful.{あいつは酷いとさえ思っていない}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:05:00.73,Homura,,0,0,0,,It's not an animal that can be held to human values, after all.{人間の価値観が通用しない生き物だから}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:05.36,Homura,,0,0,0,,No matter what, he will only repeatedly state that it is justifiable compensation for a miracle.{何もかも奇跡の正当な対価だと、そう言い張るだけよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:08.62,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That doesn't counterbalance anything at all!{全然釣り合ってないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:11.66,Madoka,,0,0,0,,He gave her a body like that...{あんな体にされちゃうなんて}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:15.62,Madoka,,0,0,0,,But Sayaka-chan simply wanted to heal the injuries of the person she loved!{さやかちゃんはただ、好きな人の怪我を治したかっただけなのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.63,Homura,,0,0,0,,There's no mistaking that it was a miracle.{奇跡であることに違いはないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.88,Homura,,0,0,0,,He made the impossible possible, after all.{不可能を可能にしたんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:27.80,Homura,,0,0,0,,Even if Miki Sayaka devoted her whole life to nursing him...{美樹さやかが一生を費やして介護しても}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:31.39,Homura,,0,0,0,,There never would have come a day when that boy could put on musical performances again.{あの少年が再び演奏できるようになる日は来なかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:37.52,Homura,,0,0,0,,A miracle, you know... In truth, it isn't something that can be bought, even with a person's life.{奇跡はね、本当なら人の命でさえ購えるものじゃないのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.65,Homura,,0,0,0,,That thing walks around selling them for that price.{それを売って歩いているのがあいつ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:44.65,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan can't go back to her original way of life?{さやかちゃんは、元の暮らしには戻れないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:49.16,Homura,,0,0,0,,I've already said it before, right? "Give up on Miki Sayaka."{前にも言ったわよね。美樹さやかのことは諦めてって}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:51.91,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan gave me aid!{さやかちゃんは私を助けてくれたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:59.17,Madoka,,0,0,0,,If Sayaka-chan wasn't a magical girl, Hitomi-chan and I would have died at that time!{さやかちゃんが魔法少女じゃなかったら、あの時、私も仁美ちゃんも死んでたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:02.17,Homura,,0,0,0,,You mustn't confuse gratitude and responsibility.{感謝と責任を混同しては駄目よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:07.68,Homura,,0,0,0,,There are absolutely no means by which you can rescue her.{貴女には彼女を救う手立てなんてない}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:10.93,Homura,,0,0,0,,Since you don't want to feel inferior, you want to do something like repay your debt... {引け目を感じたくないからって、借りを返そうだなんて}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.56,Homura,,0,0,0,,Throw away those obtrusive thoughts.{そんな出過ぎた考えは捨てなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:19.19,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Homura-chan, why are you always cold-hearted?{ほむらちゃん、どうしていつも冷たいの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:21.56,Homura,,0,0,0,,That's right...{そうね…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:25.44,Homura,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it is most likely because I'm no longer human.{きっともう人間じゃないから、かもね}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:36.75,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,With a body like this... what kind of face should I meet Kyousuke with?{こんな身体になっちゃって…私、どんな顔して恭介に会えばいいのかな}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:39.58,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}Don't sit there dejected forever, dummy.{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{いつまでもショボくれてんじゃねえぞ、ボンクラ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:53.10,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}Lemme see your mug for a bit. I have something to say.{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{ちょいと面貸しな。話がある}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:03.40,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,As I thought, you're having regrets, aren't you?{アンタさぁ、やっぱり後悔してるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.27,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,About getting this kind of body.{こんな体にされちゃったこと}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:11.78,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Y'know, I just thought, "I guess it's fine."{アタシはさぁ、まあいっかって思ってるんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:15.79,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens, I can do as I please since I've obtained this power.{何だかんだでこの力を手に入れたから好き勝手できてるわけだし}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.79,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't go as far as regretting it, y'know.{後悔するほどのことでもないってね}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:21.29,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You're just suffering the consequences of your own actions, right?{あんたは自業自得なだけでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:24.79,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,That's right, suffering the consequences of your own actions is good, y'know...{そうだよ、自業自得にしちゃえばいいのさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:28.80,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,If you only live for yourself, anything and everything is your own fault.{自分のためだけに生きてれば、何もかも自分のせいだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:32.64,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,You won't resent anyone, and there's no way you'd have something like a regret.{誰を恨むこともないし、後悔なんてあるわけがない}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:36.85,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,If you think of it that way, you can carry almost any burden, y'know.{そう思えば大抵のことは背負えるもんさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:59.12,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Bringing me all the out to a place like this, what do you want?{こんな所まで連れて来て、何の用なの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:02.75,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,It'll become a bit of a long story.{ちょっとばかり長い話になる}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.50,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Want a bite?{食うかい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:21.48,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Don't disrespect things you can eat, all right?{食い物を粗末にするんじゃねえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:22.39,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you.{殺すぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:47.54,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,This place, y'know... was my old man's church.{ここはね、アタシの親父の教会だった}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:51.55,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,A person who was too honest and excessively kind.{正直過ぎて、優し過ぎる人だった}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:55.63,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Every morning, he had an expression of sympathy each time he read the newspaper...{毎朝新聞を読む度に涙を浮かべて}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.80,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,He was the kinda person who took worries seriously, y'know. {真剣に悩んでるような人でさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:03.93,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,"To save a new era, a new creed is necessary."{新しい時代を救うには、新しい信仰が必要だって}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:06.15,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,That was my old man's saying.{それが親父の言い分だった}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:11.53,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,That's why on one occasion, he went as far as preaching things that weren't in the doctrine to worshippers. {だからある時、教義にないことまで信者に説教するようになった}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:15.03,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Of course, the worshippers' feet came to a sudden halt.{もちろん、信者の足はパッタリ途絶えたよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:17.91,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,He was also excommunicated from the main branch.{本部からも破門された}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:21.66,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,No one listened to what my old man had to say.{誰も親父の話を聞こうとしなかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:24.46,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,That's natural, isn't it?{当然だよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:27.46,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Viewing it from the outside, it'd be a suspicious-looking new religion, y'know.{傍から見れば胡散臭い新興宗教さ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:31.71,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,No matter what kind of moral or obvious things he said,{どんなに正しいこと、当たり前のことを話そうとしても}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:34.17,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,to society, he was merely someone who'd take hold of your nose.{世間じゃただの鼻つまみ者さ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:39.93,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Our whole family was left in a state where we didn't even have stuff to eat.{アタシたちは一家揃って、食う物にも事欠く有様だった}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:42.72,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,I couldn't comprehend it.{納得できなかったよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:45.48,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,My old man never said anything that was a mistake.{親父は間違ったことなんて言ってなかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:49.23,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,They were merely things that were different from what other people said, that's all.{ただ、人と違うことを話しただけだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.23,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Five minutes would be fine.{５分でいい}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:57.86,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,{\t(5818,6277,\c&H120E33&)}If they'd just properly bend an ear, anyone would have understood that he was saying things that were moral.{ちゃんと耳を傾けてくれれば、正しいこと言ってるって誰にでもわかったはずなんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:02.28,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Yet... no one would give him companionship.{なのに、誰も相手をしてくれなかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:05.29,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,It was frustrating.{悔しかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:06.33,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,It was unforgivable.{許せなかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:09.00,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,The fact that no one understood what that person was saying...{誰もあの人のことわかってくれないのが}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:11.17,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,I couldn't endure it.{アタシには我慢できなかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.59,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,That's why I relied on Kyubey.{だから、キュゥべえに頼んだんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:19.84,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,"Make everyone listen to my old man's speeches seriously."{みんなが親父の話を、真面目に聞いてくれますように、って}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:27.52,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,The next morning, my old man's church was full of commotion from a huge crowd of intrusive people.{翌朝には、親父の教会は押しかける人でごった返していた}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:31.23,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Every day, worshippers multiplied at an absolutely frightening rate.{毎日おっかなくなるほどの勢いで信者は増えていった}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:35.82,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,As for me, I openly joined the ranks of the magical girls, y'know.{アタシはアタシで、晴れて魔法少女の仲間入りさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:41.87,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,However good my old man's sermons may have been, it didn't mean they exterminated witches.{いくら親父の説法が正しくったって、それで魔女が退治できるわけじゃない}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:47.50,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,So for that part, I plunged into it wholeheartedly like an idiot, thinking, "That's where I come in!"{だからそこはアタシの出番だって、バカみたいに意気込んでいたよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:52.84,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,I thought my old man and I would save this world, both on the surface and behind the scenes.{アタシと親父で、表と裏からこの世界を救うんだって}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.88,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,But, y'know... one day, the trick was exposed to my old man.{…でもね、ある時カラクリが親父にバレた}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:06.52,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,When he learned that the crowd of worshippers weren't there simply out of faith, but were gathered by the power of magic...{大勢の信者が、ただ信仰のためじゃなく、魔法の力で集まってきたんだと知った時}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:08.10,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,my old man became enraged.{親父はブチ切れたよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:13.11,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,He spoke ill of his daughter, me, saying, "She's a witch that bewilders people's hearts."{娘のアタシを、人の心を惑わす魔女だって罵った}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:15.11,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,That makes you laugh, huh?{笑っちゃうよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:19.61,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Even though I was continuing to fight real witches every night.{アタシは毎晩、本物の魔女と戦い続けてたってのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:22.24,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,And then my old man broke.{それで親父は壊れちまった}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.24,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,The end was pitiful.{最後は惨めだったよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:29.00,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,He nearly drowned in {\i1}sake{\i0}, his mind went crazy...{酒に溺れて、頭がイカれて}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:33.67,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,It ended with a forced group suicide, taking his family against their will, y'know.{とうとう家族を道連れに、無理心中さ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:37.63,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,I was left by myself.{アタシ一人を、置き去りにしてね}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:45.10,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,My prayer had demolished my family.{アタシの祈りが、家族を壊しちまったんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:51.27,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Because I had just decided on my own to wish for another person's circumstances,{他人の都合を知りもせず、勝手な願いごとをしたせいで}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.85,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,in the end, everyone fell into misfortune.{結局誰もが不幸になった}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:56.69,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,At that time, I made a vow in my heart.{その時心に誓ったんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:59.94,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,I'd never use magic for another person's sake again.{もう二度と他人のために魔法を使ったりしない}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:04.87,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,I'd use up all of this power for nothing but my own sake.{この力は、全て自分のためだけに使い切るって}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:10.78,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Those things called miracles aren't free of charge.{奇跡ってのはタダじゃないんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:15.04,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,When you pray for hope, an equal amount of despair will spread in proportion to it.{希望を祈れば、それと同じ分だけの絶望が撒き散らされる}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:20.05,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,It reaches equilibrium and becomes zero, which is how the world holds its balance.{そうやって差し引きをゼロにして、世の中のバランスは成り立ってるんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:23.05,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Why did you want to talk to me about such a thing?{何でそんな話を私に…？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:30.81,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,You should get serious and do as you please... Living while suffering the consequences of your own actions, y'know?{アンタも開き直って好き勝手にやればいい。自業自得の人生をさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.94,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Isn't that strange?{それって変じゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:37.31,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You should be living while only thinking of your own benefit, and so...{あんたは自分のことだけ考えて生きてるはずなのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.32,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,what's your reason for worrying about me?{私の心配なんかしてくれるわけ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:44.07,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,You and I began with the same mistake.{アンタもアタシと同じ間違いから始まった}{kyouko kawaii yo, kyouko}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:49.58,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't continue a way of life that you'll regret anymore.{これ以上後悔するような生き方を続けるべきじゃない}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:53.50,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,You've already paid too high of a price in compensation.{アンタはもう対価としては高過ぎるもんを支払っちまってるんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:58.34,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,That's why, y'know... From now on, you ought to think about how to get a bit of change back.{だからさ、これからは釣り銭を取り戻すことを考えなよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:01.05,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Like you?{あんたみたいに？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:02.67,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.{そうさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:06.76,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,I understand that, while right now you continue to make mistakes.{アタシはそれを弁えてるが、アンタは今も間違い続けてる}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.55,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,I can't watch that kinda thing.{見てられないんだよ、そいつが}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:14.06,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I had various misunderstandings about you.{あんたの事、色々と誤解してた}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:16.06,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,For that, I'm sorry. I apologize.{その事はごめん。謝るよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:22.61,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,But you know, I don't regret praying for the benefit of other people.{でもね、私は人の為に祈った事を後悔してない}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:27.07,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,So that those feelings won't be lies, I've simply decided to have no regrets.{そのキモチを嘘にしない為に、後悔だけはしないって決めたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:27.95,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,From here on out, too.{これからも}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.45,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Why do you...{何でアンタ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:34.50,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You know, I don't think I've paid anything like too high of a price.{私はね、高すぎるものを支払ったなんて思ってない}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:40.50,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Depending on how I use this power, I can do as many wonderful things as I'd like with it, after all.{この力は、使い方次第でいくらでもすばらしいモノに出来るはずだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.55,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,And hey, you...{それからさ、あんた}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:47.97,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Those apples... how did you obtain them?{そのリンゴはどうやって手に入れたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.76,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,What about the money you paid to the shop?{お店で払ったお金はどうしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:56.81,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You can't say it, then.{言えないんだね}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:14:00.19,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,In that case, I won't eat those apples.{なら、私、そのリンゴは食べられない}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:02.69,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I'm not even happy to receive one.{貰っても嬉しくない}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.40,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,You freakin' idiot!{バカ野郎！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:08.91,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,We're magical girls, aren't we!?{アタシたちは魔法少女なんだぞ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:11.08,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,There isn't anyone else like us, is there!?{他に同類なんていないんだぞ！？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.91,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I will continue to fight in my own style.{私は私のやり方で戦い続けるよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:20.21,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,If that becomes a hindrance to you, then it's fine to try and kill me like before.{それがあんたの邪魔になるなら、前みたいに殺しに来ればいい}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:22.29,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I won't lose...{私は負けないし}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:24.30,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I won't bear a grudge anymore, either.{もう、恨んだりもしないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:56.50,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan, morning!{さやかちゃん、おはよう}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.75,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sayaka-san.{おはようございます、さやかさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:02.38,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Ah... yeah!{あ、ああ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:04.38,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Morning!{おはよう}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:09.13,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,What was the matter yesterday?{昨日はどうかしたんですの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:12.14,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Ah... I just felt a little sick or something, you know.{ああ、ちょっとばかり風邪っぽくてね}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:14.14,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan...{\fn\fs}{さやかちゃん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:16.85,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}It's all right. I'm fine now.{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{大丈夫だよ。もう平気}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:18.02,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona\fs57}({\fn\fs}So you don't have to worry.{\fnMona\fs57}){\fn\fs}{心配いらないから}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:22.77,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's have high spirits again today—{さーて、今日も張り切って…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:30.15,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,My, Kamijou-kun was discharged from the hospital?{あら…上条君、退院なさったんですの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:41.17,Randoms,,0,0,0,,Kamijou, are your injuries fine now?{上条、もう怪我はいいのかよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:44.92,Kamijou Touma,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If I seclude myself in my house, I won't rehabilitate, you know.{ああ。家にこもってたんじゃ、リハビリにならないしね}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:48.67,Kamijou Touma,,0,0,0,,My goal is to walk without crutches by next week or so.{来週までに松葉杖なしで歩くのが目標なんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.88,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great, Kamijou-kun?{よかったね。上条君}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.68,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Yeah...{うん}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:54.97,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan, go to him as well.{さやかちゃんも行ってきなよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.43,Madoka,,0,0,0,,You haven't spoken to him yet, right?{まだ声かけてないんでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:00.43,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I'm... fine.{私は…いいよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:16.49,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,So... what'd you want to say?{それで…話って何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:19.08,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,This is a conference regarding love.{恋の相談ですわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:25.92,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,You know, I have been keeping something a secret from Sayaka-san and Madoka-san since a while ago. {私ね、前からさやかさんやまどかさんに秘密にしてきたことがあるんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:26.96,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Eh?{え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:27.96,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,O–Okay...{う、うん}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:31.47,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,Since long ago, I...{ずっと前から…私…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:35.34,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,have loved Kamijou Kyousuke-kun dearly.{上条恭介君のこと、お慕いしてましたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:39.10,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I–Is that right?{そ、そうなんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.65,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Who'd have thought that Hitomi...{まさか仁美がねえ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:49.19,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Ah, wow, that Kyousuke guy is pretty smart and knowledgeable!{あ、なーんだ、恭介の奴、隅に置けないなあ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:52.95,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-san, you are a childhood friend of Kamijou-kun, aren't you?{さやかさんは、上条君とは幼馴染でしたわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:58.45,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, that is... You could call it an undesirable yet inseparable relationship, or... what could you call it...{あーまあ、その。腐れ縁って言うか何て言うか}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.45,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,Is that truly all there is to it?{本当にそれだけ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:08.25,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,I have decided. "I won't lie to myself anymore."{私、決めたんですの。もう自分に嘘はつかないって}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:09.46,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,What about you?{あなたはどうですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:13.97,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-san, can you face your own true feelings?{さやかさん。あなた自身の本当の気持ちと向き合えますか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:16.59,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,W–What are you talking about?{な、何の話をしてるのさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:20.19,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,You are my dear good friend.{あなたは私の大切なお友達ですわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:24.10,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,That's why... I don't want to do anything like advance ahead of you or snatch from you.{だから、抜け駆けも横取りするようなこともしたくないんですの}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:29.19,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,Concerning how much time we've had our eyes on Kamijou-kun...{上条君のことを見つめていた時間は}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.52,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,I'm surpassed by you, Sayaka-san.{私よりさやかさんの方が上ですわ}{Line is liberal, literal is more like: Compared to myself, Sayaka-san goes beyond/above[in time spent].}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:35.11,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,That's why you have the right to move forward before I do.{だから、あなたには私の先を越す権利があるべきです}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.11,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Hitomi...{仁美…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:41.12,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,I will confess my love to Kamijou-kun after school tomorrow.{私、明日の放課後に上条君に告白します}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:44.12,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,I will only wait a single full day.{丸一日だけお待ちしますわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:46.71,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-san, please decide upon a path that you will not regret.{さやかさんは後悔なさらないよう決めてください}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.59,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,Whether or not you must convey feelings to Kamijou-kun.{上条君に気持ちを伝えるべきかどうか}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:52.84,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I–I'm...{あ、あたしは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:20.99,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Madoka...{まどか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:22.91,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I come along with you?{付いてっていいかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:29.75,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to be all by yourself, Sayaka-chan. That's why...{さやかちゃんに一人ぼっちになってほしくないの。だから}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:33.88,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You... why?{あんた、何で？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:35.80,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Why do you show such kindness?{何でそんなに優しいかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:39.97,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Even when I'm not worth anything like that...{あたしにはそんな価値なんてないのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:41.64,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That's...{そんな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:45.97,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You know, I... had a regret today.{あたしね、今日後悔しそうになっちゃった}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:51.94,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,"At that time, what if I didn't save Hitomi?"{あの時、仁美を助けなければって}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:53.98,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,For just an instant, I thought about that.{ほんの一瞬だけ思っちゃった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:57.15,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I'm disqualified as an ally of justice...{正義の味方失格だよ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:00.36,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to face Mami-san.{マミさんに顔向け出来ない}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.92,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Hitomi is going to take Kyousuke!{仁美に恭介を取られちゃうよ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:14.84,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,But I can't do anything!{でも私、何も出来ない}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:18.42,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Because... I'm already dead!{だって私、もう死んでるもん}{お前はもう死んでいる}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:19.80,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I'm a zombie!{ゾンビだもん}{あとは、まそうしょうじょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:24.22,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell him to do something like hug me with this kind of body.{こんな身体で抱き締めてなんて言えない}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:26.97,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell him to do something like kiss me...{キスしてなんて言えないよ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:45.12,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I'm sorry...{ありがと。ごめんね}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:47.58,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan...{さやかちゃん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:50.46,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I'm all right now.{もう大丈夫}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.83,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That was refreshing.{スッキリしたから}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:55.50,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.{さあ、行こう}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.34,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,We have to beat witches tonight, too.{今夜も魔女をやっつけないと}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:19:58.67,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{うん}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:17.40,Homura,,0,0,0,,The fact that you're just quietly watching... is unexpected.{黙って見てるだけなんて、意外だわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:22.15,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Today's enemy isn't a familiar. She's fighting against a witch.{今日のアイツは使い魔じゃなくて魔女と戦ってる}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.57,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,It'll properly drop a Grief Seed, right?{ちゃんとグリーフシードも落とすだろ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:26.16,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,It isn't a useless hunt.{無駄な狩りじゃないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.66,Homura,,0,0,0,,You'd let her have the game for that kind of reason, would you?{そんな理由で貴女が獲物を譲るなんてね}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:37.75,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Tch, that idiot.{チッ、あのバカ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:39.21,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know how to handle it.{手こずりやがって}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:18.29,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan!{さやかちゃん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:31.52,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Seriously. I couldn't watch that.{まったく。見てらんねぇっつうの}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:34.06,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,It's fine, so pull back now.{いいからもうすっこんでなよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:35.77,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,'Cause I'll show you how it's done, all right?{手本を見せてやるからさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:37.98,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Oi!{おい}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:39.31,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way.{邪魔しないで}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:40.32,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I'll do it by myself.{一人でやれるわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:45.65,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan!{さやかちゃん}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:53.41,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,You... No way...{アンタ、まさか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:10.01,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,It's true!{ホントだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:12.81,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,If you feel like it, then anything like pain...{その気になれば痛みなんて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.85,0:22:17.56,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,can be completely cut off!{完全に消しちゃえるんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.52,0:22:25.61,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Stop... Stop already...{やめて…もう…やめて}
