Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:02.29,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That's what I decided.{私はそう決めたんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:04.00,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I don't need a reimbursement or anything.{見返りなんていらない}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:07.46,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who'll absolutely never use magic for her own benefit.{私だけは絶対に自分の為に魔法を使ったりしない}
